-- Redecard in Talks to Buy Online Payment Company, Valor Says
-- B y   T e l m a   M a r o t t o   a n d   K a t e r i n a   P e t r o f f
-- 2012-02-17T13:34:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-17/redecard-in-talks-to-buy-online-payment-company-valor-says-1-.html
Redecard SA (RDCD3)  is in talks to acquire
an e-commerce payment company, Sao Paulo-based  Valor Economico 
newspaper reported, without saying where it obtained the
information.  Redecard declined to comment, according to an e-mailed
statement sent by the press department today.  To contact the reporters on this story:
